{
  "stem": "11179.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You had to have $400 American or something, which was a-- a tremendous sum.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they allowed us to take out $4 American, which was 10 marks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so this happened in May.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, the shipping companies asked-- they-- they knew that for long before that there was move on the way to try to stop us from landing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is why they in December already 1938 wanted a round-trip ticket paid in case they had to take us back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we luckily didn't know all of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It would've driven us farther up the wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We got there in August, 10th of August.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "10th of July.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On that ship, that I'm-- no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we met, there were about 150 refugees on the ship, partially in first class, partially in tourist class.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in tour-- whatever there was available.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were about another 200 other passengers in that ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were allowed on the ship to have 400 marks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't even have that much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Per person, ship money, that you were allowed to have.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we traded the ship money with other passengers for English pounds or American dollars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they put up a notice that on a German [INAUDIBLE], the change of foreign currency is prohibited.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We found out something else which nobody seemed to have known in Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew from since my uncle was in France, you could buy the German mark in Europe for very little even in 1939.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As soon as we hit Singapore, we found out that the German money was just as good as English pound or the American dollar.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a good time to change tapes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
